snippet.textDisplay:
Jon, I am actually worried about you. I am not trying to make a joke or anything, I am honestly and truly worried.

I think this whole production you have set up is not going perfectly and although your crew seem like good people, I just don't think the format pays off. It feels so hollow!
I am not trying to say you should go back to the old days of JonTron, but back in the old videos we all enjoyed your personality so much and it was just wholesome fun. There are funny moments in your recent videos, no point denying that, but it feels more like it is funny because of the editing (cuts, titles and sfx) and the personality just shines through sometimes. Maybe it is the "being in front of the crew" part, thats in the way. I dont know. But what I do know is, that people are slowly sensing that there is something up. If you need help, please count on the support of at least a tenth of your subscribers. People who really do love you. Just let us know how we can help!

And I don't mean "buy figurines of me, so I get paid and can afford my rent!"
